Home || Tree Plants

Tree Plants Geelong

Green Turf Landscaping is a trusted supplier of tree plants in Geelong. Offering a diverse selection of high-quality tree species, they cater to residential and commercial landscaping needs. Their collection includes native and ornamental trees suited to Geelong’s climate, ensuring suitability for various environments. Green Turf Landscaping provides expert guidance on tree selection and planting, ensuring proper care and maintenance instructions are provided to clients. With a commitment to enhancing landscapes, they offer healthy and robust tree plants that contribute to the beauty and sustainability of properties across Geelong.

Get a Quote

Tree Plants installation Geelong

Tree Plants installation Services Geelong

Enhance your outdoor space with Green Turf Landscaping’s tree plant installation services in Geelong. Our expert team will help you select and plant the perfect trees to beautify and add value to your property.

What tree planting services does Green Turf Landscaping offer in Geelong?

Green Turf Landscaping provides comprehensive tree planting services in Geelong, including selecting the right species for your environment, preparing the soil, planting, and initial care instructions. We ensure that your new trees are well-suited to your landscape and thrive in their new home.

How do I choose the right trees for my property?

Our team at Green Turf Landscaping will assist you in selecting the ideal trees for your property based on factors such as soil type, climate, sun exposure, and your aesthetic preferences. We consider both the short-term and long-term impact of tree growth on your landscape.

What should I expect during the tree planting process?

During the tree planting process, Green Turf Landscaping will first assess your site to determine the best locations for planting. We then prepare the soil, dig appropriate holes, plant the trees, and provide initial care. Our team ensures that the planting is done correctly for optimal tree health and growth.

How can I care for newly planted trees?

After installation, Green Turf Landscaping will provide you with detailed care instructions for your newly planted trees. This includes information on watering, mulching, and monitoring for pests or diseases. Proper care is essential to ensure that your trees establish well and flourish.

Can Green Turf Landscaping help with the removal of existing trees before planting new ones?

Yes, Green Turf Landscaping offers tree removal services in addition to planting. If you need to remove existing trees to make way for new ones, our team can handle the removal safely and efficiently, ensuring that your site is prepared for the new plantings.
